                  <D_JUSTIFICATION>
                     <P>In January 2018, Ofwat issued a contract notice (reference: 2018/S 005-007208) using the restricted procedure under Regulation 28 of the Public Contracts Regulations 2015 (the "PCR 2015") for a Delivery Partner to support Ofwat’s 2019 Price Review. Suppliers that met the requirements set out in the Selection Questionnaire were invited to submit a tender in response to an Invitation to Tender. The tenders submitted in response to the Invitation to Tender and contract notice were incapable of being accepted, without substantial changes, in order to meet Ofwat’s needs and requirements as specified in the procurement documents. As such, to ensure that Ofwat received a tender which met the requirements specified in the procurement documents, and to ensure a continued fair, open and transparent procedure, Ofwat proceeded to award the contract using the negotiated procedure without prior publication in accordance with Regulation 32 of the PCR 2015.</P>
                  </D_JUSTIFICATION>
               </PT_NEGOTIATED_WITHOUT_PUBLICATION>
